    "description": "This API is used to automate the Cash on Delivery (COD) orders, now you can easily integrate COD API with your systems, E-Com websites from which order will be placed.\n\n<label>Prerequisites</label>\n\n1. Request parameter key names must be correct (case sensitive).\n2. Input parameter key values are not case sensitive.\n3. Subscription must be made to API product before integration.\n\n<label>Message Status</label>  \n\nReply message status can be determined from below object.\n\n<pre><code>{ \n\"returnStatus\":    { \n     \"code\": \"0200\", \n     \"status\": \"SUCCESS\", \n     \"message\": \"The operation was successful.\", \n     \"requestTime\": \"20180724111142089\", \n     \"responseTime\": \"20180724111143100\"\n  }  \n} </code></pre>\n\n| Code | Description |\n| ------ | ------ |\n| 0200 | The operation was successful. |\n| 0400 | Bad Request / Custom validation message. |\n| 0404 | Data Not Found. |\n| 0408 | The server is taking too long to respond, please try later. |\n| 0500 | An internal error has occurred. |\n\n# Authentication\n\n<!-- ReDoc-Inject: <security-definitions> -->",
